testcase.name: CMDB::HighLevelOrchrestration install saves the requested version in the currently offline group
CMDB::HighLevelOrchrestration swap makes the currently offline group online and vice versa
CMDB::HighLevelOrchrestration deploy does an install followed by a swap
CMDB::HighLevelOrchrestration deploy when only one group just upgrades the version
CMDB::HighLevelOrchrestration promotes an application from one environment to another
